===2020 census===
As of the [[2020 United States census|2020 census]], Burchinal had a population of 33, with 15 households and 5 families.<ref name="Census2020DP">{{cite web|title=2020 Decennial Census Demographic Profile (DP1)|url=https://api.census.gov/data/2020/dec/dp?get=NAME,DP1_0021P,DP1_0024P,DP1_0025C,DP1_0049C,DP1_0045C,DP1_0069C,DP1_0073C,DP1_0125P,DP1_0126P,DP1_0129P,DP1_0133P,DP1_0137P,DP1_0138P,DP1_0139P,DP1_0141P,DP1_0142P,DP1_0143P,DP1_0145P,DP1_0146P,DP1_0147C,DP1_0148C,DP1_0149C,DP1_0156C,DP1_0157C,DP1_0158C,DP1_0159P,DP1_0160P&for=place%3A09415&in=state%3A19|website=United States Census Bureau|year=2021|access-date=May 1, 2026|df=mdy}}</ref><ref name="Census2020PL">{{cite web|title=2020 Decennial Census Redistricting Data (Public Law 94-171)|url=https://api.census.gov/data/2020/dec/pl?get=NAME,P1_001N,P1_003N,P1_004N,P1_005N,P1_006N,P1_007N,P1_008N,P1_009N,P2_001N,P2_002N,H1_001N,H1_002N&for=place%3A09415&in=state%3A19|website=United States Census Bureau|year=2021|access-date=May 1, 2026|df=mdy}}</ref>

The median age was 44.5 years. About 24.2% of residents were under the age of 18 and 15.2% were 65 years of age or older. The age distribution was 24.2% under the age of 20, 0.0% from 20 to 24, 27.3% from 25 to 44, and 33.3% from 45 to 64. The gender makeup was 72.7% male and 27.3% female. For every 100 females there were 266.7 males, and for every 100 females age 18 and over there were 257.1 males age 18 and over.<ref name="Census2020DP"/>

All residents lived in rural areas.<ref name="Census2020DHC">{{cite web|title=2020 Decennial Census Demographic and Housing Characteristics (DHC)|url=https://api.census.gov/data/2020/dec/dhc?get=NAME,P2_002N,P2_003N&for=place%3A09415&in=state%3A19|website=United States Census Bureau|year=2023|access-date=May 1, 2026|df=mdy}}</ref>

There were 15 households, of which 6.7% had children under the age of 18 living in them. Of all households, 33.3% were married-couple households, 20.0% were cohabitating couples, 26.7% were households with a male householder and no spouse or partner present, and 20.0% were households with a female householder and no spouse or partner present. About 66.7% of households were non-families, 40.0% were made up of individuals, and 26.7% had someone living alone who was 65 years of age or older.<ref name="Census2020DP"/>

There were 18 housing units. The [[population density]] was 428.1 inhabitants per square mile (165.3/km<sup>2</sup>), and the housing unit density was 233.5 per square mile (90.2/km<sup>2</sup>). Of housing units, 16.7% were vacant. The homeowner vacancy rate was 22.2% and the rental vacancy rate was 0.0%.<ref name="Census2020DP"/>

